533
00:35:09,340 --> 00:35:11,881
So we go out to 50 meters, because that's kind of what

534
00:35:12,102 --> 00:35:13,262
you couldn't really afford more.

535
00:35:13,362 --> 00:35:16,463
Every game-defined send and wise that you add is extra

