538
00:35:20,185 --> 00:35:22,746
can throw at you and stuff, we're often running 900, 1,500

539
00:35:22,806 --> 00:35:25,107
sends with this system.

540
00:35:25,527 --> 00:35:27,688
So if you even just add one more, you're multiplying out,

541
00:35:27,768 --> 00:35:28,809
and it gets crazy.

542
00:35:28,889 --> 00:35:32,230
So I would have loved to have gone out to 250 meters so that

