00:35:32,250 --> 00:35:34,091
we could have done procedural echoes and everything.

544
00:35:34,131 --> 00:35:34,231
But.

545
00:35:35,686 --> 00:35:37,047
50 meters was like a good compromise.

546
00:35:39,468 --> 00:35:42,170
Then we take both the actor mixers

547
00:35:42,330 --> 00:35:43,871
and the output of the game defined sends

548
00:35:43,891 --> 00:35:45,392
and we route those through some reverbs.

549
00:35:46,213 --> 00:35:49,255
One of which is close and one of which is distant.

