557
00:36:11,493 --> 00:36:13,755
of the jitter and we average that over time.

558
00:36:14,055 --> 00:36:17,978
Then I take the output of that and I also smooth that in Wwise just because it was still

559
00:36:17,998 --> 00:36:18,778
a little too twitchy.

560
00:36:21,580 --> 00:36:28,045
And we stop ray casting at 50 meters, beyond that point where we don't have any delays

