00:37:30,788 --> 00:37:31,849
Rear reflections, gone.

588
00:37:32,129 --> 00:37:33,030
Rear reverb, gone.

589
00:37:33,530 --> 00:37:34,430
Overhead, same thing.

590
00:37:35,811 --> 00:37:37,852
And that way, so you're not folding down reflections of

